# Cloudflare Pages — URL rewrites
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Status 200 = rewrite (URL stays /lab/burn for the user, lab.html
# is served as the body). Status 301/302 = browser redirect (URL
# would change). We want rewrites so the address bar shows the
# semantic URL and bookmarks/shares land in the right mode.
#
# The lab.html JS reads the `mode` query param on load and either:
#   - skips the chooser landing → mounts the matching mode directly
#   - or shows the chooser if no mode (visiting bare /lab)
#
# Single file behind two semantic URLs — no code duplication.

/lab/burn         /lab.html?mode=burn         200
/lab/crossbreed   /lab.html?mode=crossbreed   200
